== Ezra achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Ezra'''


Ezrachem Pustok, Itihasachem Pustok chalu koxem dovorta.  Pordexi korun vhel’le thodde Judev, Babiloniek thaun portotat ani Jerusaleant novena jivit ani bhozonn sthaptat.  Heo soglleo ghoddnneo, hea sokoilea panvddeamnim manddleat  :

'''1)'''	 Persiecho  raza,  Sirus hache hukume pormannem pordesant gelolea Judevancho poilo zomo Babilonient thaun portotata.

'''2)'''	Devmondir novena bandtat ani sonvskartat, ani Devachi  bhozonn Jeruzaleak novena suru zata. 

'''3)'''	Zaitim vorsam uprant, Ezrachea fuddariponna khal Judevancho anink-ek zomo Jerusaleant portota.

Devache Somurtichi bori vollokh aslolo Ezra porjek  aplem dhormik ani somajik jivit nove manddavollir ghalunk dar dita ani he porim Israelachem otmik daiz samballta.

'''Hea pustokacho attap oso  :''' 

Pordesak  thaun poilem portonnem		1/1 – 2/70

Devmondir novena bandtar ani sonvskartat	3/1 – 6/22

Her pordexiam borabor Ezra portota		7/1 – 10/44

